title: The File on Thelma Jordon [1950] Barbara Stanwyck, Wendell Corey

sources.title: The File on Thelma Jordon [1950] Barbara Stanwyck, Wendell Corey
sources.description: The File on Thelma Jordon is a 1950 American film noir drama directed by Robert Siodmak from a screenplay by Ketti Frings. It stars Barbara Stanwyck and Wendell Corey. Â
